snippet.title: EVE Frontier Developer Deep Dive | PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
From its studio in Reykjavík, Iceland, CCP Games guides us through the ongoing development of EVE Frontier, an all-new online space survival sandbox MMO.

Founder access starts December 10th. 

Find out more at evefrontier.com/founderaccess
